  <header>
    <h2>We Create Software Solutions To Your Business Problems.</h2>
    <p>
      Quintero Systems, Inc. (formerly QuintSys, Inc) is a software development company. We specialize in creating
      technological solutions to complex business problems.
    </p>
  </header>
  <section>
    <p>
      We are involved in the design, development and deployment of large scale e-commerce systems for online retailers.
      We have been instrumental in many enterprise level applications with a strong emphasis on the research and
      implementation of lead acquisition and distribution systems
      for online marketing and online sales companies using call centers to reach their prospective clients.
    </p>
  </section>
</article>